{"tid":1395138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【8 5罷工】你嗰日返唔返工，都同我入黎！！！","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T14:53:07.000Z","uid":269084,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a7d5f54fdfb38d1e065f9254b1be43a2b4bca10","tid":1395138,"uid":269084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>罷工唔係淨係唔返工！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔返工只係一種方式，你可以請假，可以病假，可以曠工，冇問題的，都係其中一種方式。<br />\n<br />\n但大家要搞清楚，咩野係罷工！！！<br />\n<br />\n罷工唔係只係停工，<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係癱瘓系統運作。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>乜野係癱瘓系統運作？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最簡單嘅例子：巴士司機唔返工，公司搵第二個車長替你，咁你嘅唔返工就冇意義。當然你可以話，只要有足夠車長唔返工，就冇人揸車，係真嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果呢班車長，揸左架車出街，遇上不幸事故，成架車阻住條路，就令到好多人返唔到工，咁就係另一件事喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明唔明？如你嘅工作可被取締，咁你就要靠唔返工，同埋要令身邊嘅人一齊唔返工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果你嘅工作係一個累全家嘅崗位，咁你返工，跟住響工作情況下最大地影響系統運作，遠比你唔返工影響大，因為你確保左你嘅工作冇被其他人取締，仲要掌控住成個罷工情況！！！</span></span></ins></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於實際要點做，你地響自己嘅工作崗位，點樣玩死老闆，一定比我清楚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算你唔返工，都可以幫手癱瘓其他系統㗎，所以唔好hea，出去做野！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，需要的話，緊跟司長呼籲，緊守工作崗位啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（返到公司咪係守住左個工作崗位囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"b16a6e000230e7e3e1e164b7de76dc9421d1fdc2","tid":1395138,"uid":269084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6cbcce9f83808afffd88a181005b94c97ae24ac","tid":1395138,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1395073/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1395073/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n尋晚反應非常熱烈，今晚繼續"},{"pid":"ed14de59fc4609c4d8a00317b6d8d9bdde0ebc68","tid":1395138,"uid":269084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:30:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2114703ffe0ffd5054f745a70f081d3b3f3912af","tid":1395138,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:30:46.000Z","msg":"塞地鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2ee5bba59a556f14160cd7700d98b2a405d34f","tid":1395138,"uid":269084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T21:26:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2dc791588b0124fdac929fe6ff92f7776723052","tid":1395138,"uid":293619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T22:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNdX1dy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.